<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/GO_0005575> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Note that, in addition to forming the root of the cellular component ontology, this term is recommended for the annotation of gene products whose cellular component is unknown. When this term is used for annotation, it indicates that no information was available about the cellular component of the gene product annotated as of the date the annotation was made; the evidence code 'no data' (ND), is used to indicate this." .
