<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/GO_0071871> <http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasExactSynonym> "response to epinephrine stimulus" .
<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/GO_0071871> <http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasOBONamespace> "biological_process" .
<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/GO_0071871> <http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#id> "GO:0071871" .
<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/GO_0071871> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Note that epinephrine and norepinephrine are ligands for the same receptors, and there are multiple adrenergic receptors." .
<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/GO_0071871> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "response to epinephrine" .
